parameters: This area exuded an atmosphere different from the others.

The sky was clear, the wind gentle, and the scent of flowers
wafted from the large trees, which emanated strength and a
mystical power.

Luna was overwhelmed by this space when... a "voice" could
be heard from somewhere.

Can you hear me... I am speaking directly to your heart
right now.

I am the great tree before you... the spirit of the World
Tree... that might be an easier way for you to understand.
Let me explain this place to you, as it's your first visit.

While Luna was stunned by a phenomenon she had never
experienced before, the so-called spirit of the World Tree
continued its tale.

This is a place where you can bring about changes in your
relationships with the "men" around you.

Hearing such unbelievable words, Luna found it hard to
believe, but having already witnessed strange phenomena, she
had no choice but to believe.

The relationships you have built up until now, whether you
desire them or not...

I shall "adjust" any relationships that have gone too far or
pure love that has begun to fade, to help you walk towards
your ideal future.

If there are any relationships that come to mind, please
choose them.

It seems that Luna can increase or decrease her intimacy
with the men she is involved with.

Please be aware that adjusting these values will affect the
ending route you take.

We meet again. Let me help you adjust your romantic
relationships.
